{
  "texts": [
    "This computation involves considering the speed of the medium, c (line 4), which is calculated based on the variance of the input sequence, V ( -→ x).",
    "Additionally, the speed of the source, v s (line 5), is determined by multiplying the true label, y, with the absolute value of the variance of V ( -→ x).",
    "The speed of the receiver, v r (line 6), is set to a fixed value of 0.8.",
    "The source frequency, E f0 (line 7), is obtained by using the function SourceFrequency(V ( -→ x))on the input embedding V ( -→ x).",
    "The observer's frequency, E f (line 8), is computed as c+vr c-vs E f0."
  ]
}